{"word":"H7433 - רָמֹת גִּלעָד - Râmôth Gilʻâd - raw-moth' gil-awd' - Ramoth-gilead","slug":"H7433","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָמֹת גִּלעָד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Râmôth Gilʻâd"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-moth' gil-awd'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ramoth-gilead"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>רמות גּלעד רמת גּלעד</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>râmôth gil‛âd râmôth gil‛âd</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>raw-moth'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Ramoth = \"heights\" <ol><li>an Israelite who had a foreign wife in the time of Ezra (noun proper masculine)</li><li>Ramoth-gilead - a place in Gilead (noun proper locative)<ol type='a'><li>site dubious</li></ol></li></ol> <p />Origin: from the pl. of <a href=\"#/H7413\">H7413</a> and <a href=\"#/H1568\">H1568</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4791\">H4791</a>, <a href=\"#/H7216\">H7216</a>, <a href=\"#/H7311\">H7311</a>, <a href=\"#/H7312\">H7312</a>, <a href=\"#/H7315\">H7315</a>, <a href=\"#/H7316\">H7316</a>, <a href=\"#/H7317\">H7317</a>, <a href=\"#/H7318\">H7318</a>, <a href=\"#/H7319\">H7319</a>, <a href=\"#/H7320\">H7320</a>, <a href=\"#/H7410\">H7410</a>, <a href=\"#/H7413\">H7413</a>, <a href=\"#/H7414\">H7414</a>, <a href=\"#/H7418\">H7418</a>, <a href=\"#/H7419\">H7419</a>, <a href=\"#/H7427\">H7427</a>, <a href=\"#/H7432\">H7432</a>, <a href=\"#/H7434\">H7434</a>, <a href=\"#/H7435\">H7435</a>, <a href=\"#/H7437\">H7437</a>, <a href=\"#/H8641\">H8641</a>, <a href=\"#/H8642\">H8642</a>"}]}